pull.title: Add Hebrew wordlist to BIP39
pull.body:
An exciting step to make blockchain technology accessible for Hebrew native speakers.

All words are manually reviewed by native speakers in addition to python script which verified length, order and 4-characters rule.

Hebrew wordlist rules:

1. Common and simple words in Hebrew.
2. Only words with 4-8 letters.
3. Words can be uniquely determined by typing the first 4 characters.
4. No personal names or geographical names.
5. No offensive or negative words.
6. If both female/male words are available, choose only one version.
